  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Andaman & Nicobar</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">The islands have a tropical climate — warm year-round (23–33°C). November to April is ideal — calm seas, clear skies, excellent visibility for diving (30m+). May to October brings the southwest monsoon with rough seas and limited ferry services. The northeast monsoon (October-November) is milder. December-January is peak season — book accommodation well in advance.</p>
