  <h2 class="sec-title" id="distTitle">Every District of <em>Andaman & Nicobar</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="distNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">The archipelago is divided into 3 districts — North & Middle Andaman (the island chain's heart), South Andaman (with Port Blair, the capital) and Nicobar (the southern islands, largely restricted). The Nicobar Islands require special permits and most areas are off-limits to protect the indigenous Nicobarese and Shompen communities.</p>
